The salmon springs, the lintel rings.

38
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,159
Xuanzhi.

39
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,840
Why is this place so eerie?

40
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,800
Does the Night Emperor

41
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,439
look like a ghost?

42
00:03:31,719 --> 00:03:33,919
How rude you are!

43
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:38,800
Xuanzhi.

44
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,400
He is the Night Emperor?

45
00:03:43,599 --> 00:03:44,879
You're so prestige,

46
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:45,919
knowing all affairs.

47
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,159
We aren't coming

48
00:03:47,159 --> 00:03:47,800
to offend you,

49
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:48,639
but to

50
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,879
seek answers.

51
00:03:51,039 --> 00:03:51,800
With a reward.

52
00:03:52,039 --> 00:03:53,639
You are quite sensible.

53
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,879
We want to ask what this is.

54
00:04:04,479 --> 00:04:05,879
It became a cocoon.

55
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:08,800
First in larval state,

56
00:04:09,199 --> 00:04:10,400
later self-entombed in cocoon.

57
00:04:14,479 --> 00:04:16,079
This is the Mother-Child Worm.

58
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:18,199
Common in Miaojiang.

59
00:04:18,879 --> 00:04:22,160
It is cultivated within
human or animal corpses.

60
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,920
Mother and Child worms
share consciousness.

61
00:04:25,519 --> 00:04:27,000
By controlling the Mother Worm,

62
00:04:27,319 --> 00:04:29,519
the Child Worm miles away

63
00:04:29,519 --> 00:04:30,920
can control their hosts.

64
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,079
Thus, enabling

65
00:04:32,079 --> 00:04:33,519
kill without trace.

66
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:36,519
But breeding them is arduous.

67
00:04:36,959 --> 00:04:39,279
It's lost to the world for 30 years.

68
00:04:40,279 --> 00:04:41,199
Yet now,

69
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:43,240
it shows up again.

70
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:48,000
Why is it like this now?

71
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:53,120
This is your second question.

72
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:05,079
The Mother Worm controlling it died,

73
00:05:05,079 --> 00:05:06,560
so it cocoons

74
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:08,959
to transition from Child to Mother.

75
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,439
Yet this Child Worm

76
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:16,040
wouldn't transition successfully.

77
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,160
Why?

78
00:05:27,279 --> 00:05:29,079
Normally, they should be

79
00:05:29,639 --> 00:05:32,000
robust and plump.

80
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:36,319
Yet this cocoon indicates

81
00:05:36,399 --> 00:05:37,639
its undersized form

82
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,240
and stunted growth.

83
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,639
After transition,

84
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:43,000
it cannot spawn many Child Worms.

85
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:45,000
This cocoon

86
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,319
isn't pure white,

87
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,439
but with pale yellow.

88
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,079
I guess

89
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:53,600
long-term drug exposure

90
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:56,920
severed the link
between Mother and Child worms.

91
00:05:57,319 --> 00:05:58,360
The Mother Worm's death

92
00:05:59,079 --> 00:06:00,399
triggered its cocooning.

93
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,240
What about this?

94
00:06:16,439 --> 00:06:17,240
Immortal's Ecstasy,

95
00:06:17,879 --> 00:06:20,079
a rare drug that induces
hallucinations and numbness.

96
00:06:20,439 --> 00:06:22,920
Once diluted, it paralyzes.

97
00:06:23,839 --> 00:06:25,000
This worm

98
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:27,319
suffered prolonged exposure.

99
00:06:27,759 --> 00:06:28,480
Hence,

100
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:30,920
it failed to kill the host promptly.

101
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:33,439
So,

102
00:06:33,839 --> 00:06:34,759
the Judicial Minister

103
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,720
consumed the Immortal's Ecstasy

104
00:06:37,199 --> 00:06:38,120
that made him

105
00:06:38,519 --> 00:06:39,759
to avoid dying with the others.

106
00:07:04,319 --> 00:07:04,959
Ling.

107
00:07:06,639 --> 00:07:07,240
It's cold.

108
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:08,920
Don't catch a chill.

109
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:10,879
Go get some rest.

110
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:13,920
I'm okay.

111
00:07:14,399 --> 00:07:15,040
Not tired yet.

112
00:07:33,639 --> 00:07:34,079
Ling.

113
00:07:34,759 --> 00:07:35,600
I love you.

114
00:07:36,879 --> 00:07:38,040
Let me be your support.

115
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:39,680
Okay?

116
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,040
X-Xuanzhi.

117
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,240
I appreciate your love.

118
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,639
All these years,

119
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,240
you've excused my faults,

120
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:50,560
tolerated my moods,

121
00:07:51,279 --> 00:07:52,360
and enabled all my choices.

122
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,720
But I can't marry you.

123
00:07:56,399 --> 00:07:56,959
Ling.

124
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,519
I did all that willingly.

125
00:08:00,639 --> 00:08:02,439
My greatest happiness is to marry you.

126
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:04,720
Moreover,

127
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,000
if you don't marry me,

128
00:08:07,399 --> 00:08:08,120
I fear the court

129
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,720
will soon involve you in a political

130
00:08:09,959 --> 00:08:11,040
marriage alliance.

131
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,000
Wu Ya'er.

132
00:08:18,759 --> 00:08:19,560
Want to kill me?

133
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:21,759
How dare you try to kiss her.

134
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,120
Deserve death.

135
00:08:24,399 --> 00:08:25,160
Wu Ya'er,

136
00:08:26,199 --> 00:08:27,120
stop acting rashly.

137
00:08:28,639 --> 00:08:29,920
What do you mean?

138
00:08:30,199 --> 00:08:30,720
My lady,

139
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,480
he's acting rashly.

140
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:34,440
Don't you see

141
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,440
she doesn't want it?

142
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,759
Is this your Guo family's discipline?

143
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,559
My Guo family's discipline

144
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,559
