145
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:42,399
to judge.

146
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:43,840
Besides,

147
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,679
I'm Ling's betrothed.

148
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,360
Why do you interfere?

149
00:08:53,279 --> 00:08:54,080
Enough!

150
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:58,399
Xuanzhi,

151
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,360
what do you mean?

152
00:09:00,759 --> 00:09:01,720
I heard from Father

153
00:09:02,016 --> 00:09:03,159
that the Emperor still wants

154
00:09:03,159 --> 00:09:04,519
a political marriage with Youzhou.

155
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,159
What if he sends you...

156
00:09:06,159 --> 00:09:06,919
Enough.

157
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,000
I understand.

158
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,080
Know what you did wrong?

159
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,080
I did nothing wrong.

160
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,679
Anyone who dares disrespect you

161
00:09:20,279 --> 00:09:21,080
deserves death.

162
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:22,240
Wu Ya'er!

163
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:24,759
Forgot what you promised me?

164
00:09:25,399 --> 00:09:26,399
You vowed to protect me

165
00:09:26,919 --> 00:09:27,840
and those around me.

166
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,159
Forgot all these?

167
00:09:30,519 --> 00:09:31,200
I didn't.

168
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:31,960
But...

169
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:33,200
Enough.

170
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,679
Don't you keep your promises?

171
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,039
No.

172
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,399
Now shake hands and make peace.

173
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:44,879
He wanted to kill me.

174
00:09:45,519 --> 00:09:46,759
And I make peace with him?

175
00:09:46,759 --> 00:09:48,120
Don't you listen to me?

176
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:04,639
Go rest.

177
00:10:05,279 --> 00:10:06,759
We'll investigate the worm tomorrow.

178
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:31,039
Why is Wu Ya'er

179
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:32,320
kneeling there?

180
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,159
No idea.

181
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:34,960
Been kneeling all night.

182
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:37,559
Seems he does it voluntarily.

183
00:10:40,639 --> 00:10:41,279
You may go.

184
00:10:41,519 --> 00:10:42,279
- Yes.
- Yes.

