191
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:10,440
Deserve it.

192
00:11:10,639 --> 00:11:12,159
So you use this trick

193
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:13,519
to make me pity you?

194
00:11:14,399 --> 00:11:14,799
No.

195
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:15,919
It's my fault,

196
00:11:16,399 --> 00:11:17,399
failing to keep my word.

197
00:11:19,279 --> 00:11:20,159
I was wrong.

198
00:11:23,039 --> 00:11:23,799
Okay.

199
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:25,720
Don't do this again.

200
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:26,919
Understood?

201
00:11:27,679 --> 00:11:28,240
Understood.

202
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:30,320
Get up.

203
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:37,919
I told you to get up.

204
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,399
Now it hurts?

205
00:12:09,519 --> 00:12:10,639
Come sit and eat.

206
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:24,159
You've grown crafty.

207
00:12:24,639 --> 00:12:25,720
Used a trick to earn pity.

208
00:12:26,279 --> 00:12:27,639
Your memories are missing,

209
00:12:28,039 --> 00:12:29,080
but you're still scheming.

210
00:12:29,159 --> 00:12:29,799
Xuanzhi.

211
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:30,960
Enough.

212
00:12:32,039 --> 00:12:33,159
What about the worm thing?

213
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:34,399
I tweaked

214
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:36,440
the Mother Worm rig in the Black Market.

215
00:12:37,856 --> 00:12:39,900
It'll warn us if the one
to cast the worm is nearby.

216
00:12:40,279 --> 00:12:40,759
Then,

217
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:41,919
we could capture him

218
00:12:42,159 --> 00:12:42,879
right away.

219
00:12:49,279 --> 00:12:50,639
He killed my sister.

220
00:12:51,799 --> 00:12:53,320
I'll end him myself.

221
00:12:58,848 --> 00:13:00,679
(Memorial)

222
00:13:00,679 --> 00:13:02,039
Never thought beyond Shendu

223
00:13:02,039 --> 00:13:03,639
lay such a desolate place.

224
00:13:04,288 --> 00:13:05,448
After the foreign invasion,

225
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:07,639
though Shendu remains prosperous,

226
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:09,159
many places

227
00:13:09,519 --> 00:13:10,360
have declined.

228
00:13:11,639 --> 00:13:13,200
Shendu is maintained

229
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:14,679
by draining the whole realm.

230
00:13:15,279 --> 00:13:16,720
Are you sure Jinlouzi is here?

231
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:18,000
Yes.

232
00:13:18,559 --> 00:13:20,200
The Mother Worm points this way.

233
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:21,720
Further north

234
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,000
lies Youzhou territory.

235
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:25,519
Xuanzhi,

236
00:13:26,440 --> 00:13:27,600
what custom is this?

237
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,600
No idea.

238
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:31,320
White lanterns

239
00:13:32,039 --> 00:13:32,879
and coffins.

240
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:34,919
Eerie.

241
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:36,240
Xuanzhi,

242
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,879
let's leave. I'm scared.

243
00:13:38,679 --> 00:13:39,600
That's all you say?

244
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:41,080
I'm here, fear not.

245
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:42,600
Right.

246
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:48,000
A living person?

247
00:13:51,279 --> 00:13:51,639
Old man.

248
00:13:52,279 --> 00:13:52,759
Old man.

249
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:54,360
Old man.

250
00:13:57,879 --> 00:13:58,480
Leave now.

251
00:13:58,559 --> 00:13:59,000
Leave!

252
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:00,240
Mr. Immortal's coming.

253
00:14:00,879 --> 00:14:01,559
Mr. Immortal?

254
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:03,600
You folks are new?

255
00:14:03,799 --> 00:14:04,320
Yeah.

256
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:06,279
Please enlighten us.

257
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:08,679
That's my father.

258
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:09,360
He's ill.

259
00:14:09,380 --> 00:14:10,840
Mr. Immortal will take him to heal.

260
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:11,879
Leave now.

261
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:13,879
Don't get in the way.

262
00:14:14,400 --> 00:14:15,000
Go now.

263
00:14:40,790 --> 00:14:46,816
