266
00:14:58,086 --> 00:15:00,559
♪Unease fills the people's hearts♪

267
00:15:00,949 --> 00:15:07,307
♪Darkness looms with impending doom♪

268
00:15:08,246 --> 00:15:14,486
♪A lone hero casts life and death aside♪

269
00:15:15,373 --> 00:15:21,390
