♪Through any crowd,
I'd find my way to you♪

273
00:15:42,629 --> 00:15:48,838
♪Through every trial and fear,
I'll see you through♪

274
00:15:49,518 --> 00:15:56,733
♪Till dust at last,
within your heart finds rest♪

275
00:15:57,005 --> 00:16:02,910
♪Never to part, whatever betide♪

276
00:16:03,363 --> 00:16:10,006
♪Through any crowd,
I'd find my way to you♪

277
00:16:10,435 --> 00:16:16,674
♪Our love transcends the worldly storm♪

278
00:16:17,155 --> 00:16:26,513
♪Yearning burns as snow melts,
mists clear away♪

279
